#: ../../source/auth/saml.rst:2
msgid "SAML"
msgstr "SAML"

#: ../../source/auth/saml.rst:5
msgid "简介"
msgstr "Introduction"

#: ../../source/auth/saml.rst:6
msgid ""
"SAML (Security Assertion Markup Language) "
"译为安全断言标记语言，是一种xXML格式的语言，使用XML格式交互，来完成SSO的功能。"
msgstr ""
"SAML (Security Assertion Markup Language) is an XML-based language that uses "
"XML-formatted exchanges to implement SSO."

#: ../../source/auth/saml.rst:8
msgid "SAML存在1.1和2.0两个版本，这两个版本不兼容，不过在逻辑概念或者对象结构上大致相当，只是在一些细节上有所差异。"
msgstr ""
"SAML has two versions, 1.1 and 2.0. These versions are incompatible, but they"
" are broadly similar in logical concepts and object structure, with "
"differences in some details."

#: ../../source/auth/saml.rst:11
msgid "认证过程"
msgstr "Authentication Process"

#: ../../source/auth/saml.rst:12
msgid "SAML的认证涉及到三个角色，分别为服务提供者(SP)、认证服务(IDP)、用户(Client)。一个比较典型认证过程如下："
msgstr ""
"SAML authentication involves three roles: the Service Provider (SP), the "
"Identity Provider (IdP), and the user (Client). A typical authentication "
"process is as follows:"

#: ../../source/auth/saml.rst:14
msgid "Client访问受保护的资源"
msgstr "The Client accesses a protected resource"

#: ../../source/auth/saml.rst:15
msgid "SP生成认证请求SAML返回给Client"
msgstr "The SP generates an authentication request SAML message and returns it to the Client"

#: ../../source/auth/saml.rst:16
msgid "Client提交请求到IDP"
msgstr "The Client submits the request to the IdP"

#: ../../source/auth/saml.rst:17
msgid "IDP返回认证请求"
msgstr "The IdP returns an authentication request"

#: ../../source/auth/saml.rst:18
msgid "Client登陆IDP"
msgstr "The Client logs in to the IdP"

#: ../../source/auth/saml.rst:19
msgid "认证成功后，IDP生成私钥签名标识了权限的SAML，返回给Client"
msgstr ""
"After authentication succeeds, the IdP generates a SAML assertion indicating "
"the permissions, signs it with the private key, and returns it to the Client"

#: ../../source/auth/saml.rst:20
msgid "Client提交SAML给SP"
msgstr "The Client submits the SAML assertion to the SP"

#: ../../source/auth/saml.rst:21
msgid "SP读取SAML，确定请求合法，返回资源"
msgstr "The SP reads the SAML assertion, determines that the request is valid, and returns the resource"

#: ../../source/auth/saml.rst:24
msgid "安全问题"
msgstr "Security Issues"

#: ../../source/auth/saml.rst:25
msgid "源于ssl模式下的认证可选性，可以删除签名方式标签绕过认证"
msgstr ""
"Because authentication can be optional in SSL mode, deleting the signature "
"method tag may bypass authentication"

#: ../../source/auth/saml.rst:26
msgid "如果SAML中缺少了expiration，并且断言ID不是唯一的，那么就可能被重放攻击影响"
msgstr ""
"If expiration is missing from SAML and assertion IDs are not unique, the "
"implementation may be affected by replay attacks"

